    ht.mem_of_nhds_within_ne_bot <| ha.mono <| le_trans‚Çì hstf (le_principal_iff.2 (inter_subset_right _ _))
  exact ‚ü®a, ‚ü®hsa, this‚ü©, ha‚ü©

/-- The intersection of a closed set and a compact set is a compact set. -/
